,Recommended,262260,9162593,"Posted: 17 February, 2014",all,CueZero,"Probably the best non-Japanese shmup ever created, Jets n Guns easily earns it's reputation as being one of the most addictive and diverse shooters in the genre.The game is a classic shooter that plays horizontally similar to classic horishmups such as Metal Black, Einhander, or the legendary Gradius and R-type series but is very different with it's colorful, creative, and humorous comicbook style. Oh, and just about the raddest and baddest soundtrack you'll ever hear for a videogame.Jets N Guns Gold has by far more content and challenge to offer than just about any shooter before it, with a campaign that took me at least a year to complete on Normal.  This is a game you'll want to play multiple times, and upgrades/weapons carry over, so beating it on Easy is only the beginning.The challenge is there in full force but without being too impossible for newcomers thanks to a hugely robust weapon catalogue and upgrade system, all it takes is a little tinkering and you'll be on your way to becoming a Jets N Guns master!"
